high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right and move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Slice the tomato in the bin.
Put the knife in the bin.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the bin.
Turn right, move to in front of the refrigerator.
Put the tomato slice in the refrigerator, chill it, pick it back up.
Turn right and move to the bin at the end of the counter.
Put the tomato slice in the bin.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of tomato into a bin.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter on the left of the refrigerator.
Pick up the yellow knife on the left of the large glass.
Turn right and go to the trash can in the right corner across the kitchen.
Slice the red tomato inside the trash can.
Place the knife inside the trash can.
Pick up one slice of the tomato out of the trash can.
Turn right and go to the front of the refrigerator.
Chill the slice of tomato next to the gray plate in the refrigerator and take it out.
Turn around and go back to the trash can in the right corner.
Place the tomato slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out the chilled slice of tomato with the knife.

high_descs: Turn left, turn right, go past the sink to the counter across the room
Pick up the knife with yellow handle
Turn around to go to the opposite end of the room toward a gray bin with a tomato
Aim the knife at the tomato
Strike the tomato with knife
Pick up a slice of tomato from the bin
Take the slice of the tomato to the fridge
Open the fridge, put the tomato slice on the tray, close the fridge, wait for a few seconds, and take the slice out of the fridge
Go back to the gray bin
Put the slice of the tomato in the bin
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of tomato in the bin
